title: Jankovic beats Venus Williams in Hong Kong Open semifinals
text: Photo: Kin Cheung, AP Venus Williams of the United States hits a return shot against Jelena Jankovic of Serbia during their semifinal match at the WTA Hong Kong Open tennis tournament in Hong Kong, Saturday, Oct. 17, 2015. Venus Williams of the United States hits a return shot against... HONG KONG (AP) — Venus Williams saw her chance of qualifying for the season-ending WTA Finals slip away Saturday after losing in straight sets to Jelena Jankovic of Serbia in the semifinals of the Hong Kong Open.
